# Laravel Cloud (RealSmart suite)

## CLI

```bash
composer global require laravel/cloud-cli
export PATH="$HOME/.composer/vendor/bin:$PATH"
cloud auth   # browser — run in your terminal
```

Per-repo: `cloud repo:config` (commit `.cloud/config.json`).

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Deploy | `cloud deploy` |
| Logs | `cloud environment:logs` |
| Artisan | `cloud command:run "php artisan migrate --force"` |

## Flux Pro on Cloud

Env vars: `FLUX_USERNAME`, `FLUX_LICENSE_KEY`  
Build command (before `composer install`):

```bash
composer config http-basic.composer.fluxui.dev "$FLUX_USERNAME" "$FLUX_LICENSE_KEY"
```

